    • suppressHistoricalSnapshots

      public TableMetadata.Builder suppressHistoricalSnapshots()
      Suppresses snapshots that are historical, removing the metadata for lazy snapshot loading.

      Note that the snapshots are not considered removed from metadata and no RemoveSnapshot changes are created.

      A snapshot is historical if no ref directly references its ID.

      Returns:
      this for method chaining
